Package: strapwise
Title: Bootstrap Inference and Response Curves for Logistic Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Justin", "Wilkins", email = "justin.wilkins@occams.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides case-resampling bootstrap for fitted binomial GLMs,
    returning percentile confidence intervals for all model coefficients.
    A companion plotting function generates marginal response curves for
    continuous predictors (probability curve with bootstrap CI ribbon and
    observed-outcome jittered points) and predicted-probability plots for categorical
    predictors (dot + error bars), with observed binary outcomes overlaid
    as jittered points on both plot types.
